title: Snaps - Are Georgia, Clemson, LSU & USC overrated or underrated in AP Poll rankings, Deion Rumors
itunes:title: Snaps - Are Georgia, Clemson, LSU & USC overrated or underrated in AP Poll rankings, Deion Rumors
description:
T-Bob Hebert and Aaron Murray discuss whether Kirby Smart and Georgia, Dabo Swinney and Clemson, Brian Kelly and LSU, or Lincoln Riley and USC are overrated or underrated by the AP Poll. They later discuss Deion Sanders to Georgia Tech rumors and Aaron shares his top 5 quarterbacks from week 4 of college football. #volume #colincowherd #herd
